        TO_BE_COMPLETELY_TRUTHFUL_I_AM_HEARTBROKEN_TO                         = 7564,  -- To be completely truthful, I am heartbroken to be giving up the %, the most famous of instruments, even to a fellow bard.
        BUT_AN_INSTRUMENT_ONLY_SHOWS_ITS_TRUE_WORTH                           = 7565,  -- But an instrument only shows its true worth when being played. This horn should be delighted to be passed on to such a talent as yourself.
        SHE_HAS_A_CAPRICIOUS_SOUL_BUT_DO_TREAT                                = 7566,  -- She has a capricious soul, but do treat her well. And do not forget that even without a raging battle, you can still play a tune for the simple enjoyment of those around you...
        ID_7567                                                               = 7567,  -- ...
        HE_WAS_A_WONDERFUL_PERFORMER                                          = 7568,  -- He was a wonderful performer.
        LET_US_BE_ON_OUR_WAY_OUR_TOUR                                         = 7569,  -- Let us be on our way. Our tour of the world has only just begun...
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_OUT_OF_THE_ORDINARY_HERE_5                           = 7570,  -- There is nothing out of the ordinary here.
        YOUR_BODY_GOES_NUMB_WITH_DREAD                                        = 7571,  -- Your body goes numb with dread!
        TH_THAT_S                                                             = 7572,  -- Th-that's...!
        HEY_HEY_ARE_YOU_ALL_RIGHT                                             = 7573,  -- Hey... Hey! Are you all right!?
        HEY_C_MON_HANG_IN_THERE                                               = 7574,  -- Hey! C'mon, hang in there!
        UGH_HUH_Y_YOU_ARE_OH_SO_YOU                                           = 7575,  -- Ugh... Huh? Y-you are...? Oh... ...So you're safe...
        OW_P_PATHETIC                                                         = 7576,  -- ...Ow! P-pathetic...
        I_M_SORRY_I_M_REALLY_SORRY_I                                          = 7577,  -- I'm sorry... I'm really sorry! I left you alone to save my own skin...
        HEH_DON_T_LET_IT_BOTHER_YOU_YOU                                       = 7578,  -- ...Heh... Don't...let it bother you... You'd have to be a crazy bastard...to be unafraid of a beast like that.
        M_MORE_IMPORTANTLY_YOU_RE_SAFE                                        = 7579,  -- M-more importantly... You're...safe...
        IMAGINE_IF_YOU_WOULD_VE_STAYED_AND_BEEN                               = 7580,  -- Imagine if you would've stayed and been done in yourself... What a joke that would be...
        WHAT_HAVE_I_DONE_HOW_COULD_I_HAVE                                     = 7581,  -- What have I done...? How could I have let this happen...!?
        HEH_DON_T_WORRY_ABOUT_IT                                              = 7582,  -- ...Heh... Don't worry about it...
        ACTUALLY_LONG_AGO_SOMEONE_SAVED_ME_TOO                                = 7583,  -- Actually... Long ago, someone saved me, too.
        DAMMIT_IT_S_TOO_STRONG                                                = 7584,  -- Dammit! It's too strong!
        JUST_WHEN_I_THOUGHT_I_WAS_DONE_FOR                                    = 7585,  -- Just when I thought I was done for, a man appeared out of the blue and rescued me...
        BUT_AS_SOON_AS_I_WAS_FREE_FROM                                        = 7586,  -- But as soon as I was free from the monster, I grew afraid. I also ran away, leaving my rescuer behind.
        AHH_H_HELP_ME                                                         = 7587,  -- Ahh...!!! H-help me!!!
        WHEN_I_BEGAN_TO_WONDER_ABOUT_THE_MAN                                  = 7588,  -- When I began to wonder about the man and turned around, he was already lying in a bloody heap. He had given his life to save mine...
        HE_MADE_ME_WANT_TO_USE_MY_POWER                                       = 7589,  -- He made me want to use my power to help others... No, he showed me that using the strength we have for the sake of others is our duty...
        I_HAVE_A_FAVOR_TO_ASK_OF_YOU                                          = 7590,  -- I have a favor to ask of you...
        TAKE_THIS_SWORD                                                       = 7591,  -- Take...this sword...
        I_I_WANT_YOU_TO_BURY_THIS_SWORD                                       = 7592,  -- I...I want you to bury this sword with me. It's my treasure...the sword of the man who rescued me.
        WITH_THIS_I_CAN_I_CAN_FINALLY_ATONE                                   = 7593,  -- With this...I can...I can finally...atone...for my sin... Please...let me...sleep now...
        NO_WAKE_UP_DON_T_GO_NO                                                = 7594,  -- No! Wake up! Don't go! No...!!!
        HOLD_OUT_YOUR_HAND_YES_NO                                             = 7595,  -- Hold out your hand? Yes. No.
        YEAH_WHADDAYA_WANT_KUPO                                               = 7596,  -- Yeah? Whaddaya want, kupo?
        YER_LOOKIN_FOR_THE_BOSS_Y_SAY_LOOKS                                   = 7597,  -- Yer lookin' for the boss, y'say? Looks like it ain't your lucky day. He just left.
        WHERE_D_HE_GO_Y_SAY_HAH_AS                                            = 7598,  -- Where'd he go, y'say? Hah! As if I'd tell a punk like you, kupo!
        I_MEAN_IF_THE_BOSS_CAUGHT_ME_BLABBIN                                  = 7599,  -- I mean, if the boss caught me blabbin' to everyone 'n their uncle about his favorite huntin' spot past the Sahagins' ornamented door, I'd be cruisin' for a serious bruisin'. So scram!
        YEAH_I_M_RIKO_ALL_RIGHT_WHAT_S                                        = 7600,  -- Yeah, I'm Riko all right. What's it to ya, kid?
        YOU_WANT_ME_TO_LEND_YA_HOW_MUCH                                       = 7601,  -- ...!? You want me to lend ya how much!?
        WHAT_S_A_LITTLE_BOY_GIRL_LIKE_YOU                                     = 7602,  -- What's a little boy/girl] like you gonna do with that kind o' cash? Eh? I ain't one to talk, but sounds to me like you're up to no good.
        WHAT_THAT_SNOT_NOSED_TOTO_KUPELIAURE_IS_TRYING                        = 7603,  -- What!? That snot-nosed Toto Kupeliaure is trying to privatize the Mog Houses, you say?
        AND_HE_S_BILLING_YOU_FOR_YEARS_OF                                     = 7604,  -- ...And he's billing you for years of unpaid rent!?
        HAH_WELL_THAT_S_WHAT_I_VE_BEEN                                        = 7605,  -- Hah. Well, that's what I've been saying all along. Those Kupeliaures are born with a silver spoon in their mouths. Leave the operation to them and nothin' good will come of it.
        BUT_DON_T_WORRY_KID_UNCLE_RIKO_S                                      = 7606,  -- But don't worry, kid. Uncle Riko's got ya covered.
        YOU_VE_GOT_YOURSELF_A_LOAN_WE_LL                                      = 7607,  -- You've got yourself a loan. We'll give the Kupeliaure brat what he's asking for...heh heh heh.
        WHAT_YOU_THOUGHT_YOU_D_BE_GETTIN_CASH                                 = 7608,  -- What, you thought you'd be gettin' cash? I don't think so. We'll be keepin' this deal on the down-low, ya see? This draft is good for all the gil Toto asked ya for. And you're gonna carry it so that nobody's gonna see even a bulge in your pocket. Got it?
        ANYWAY_I_LL_BE_GETTIN_MY_PEOPLE_ON                                    = 7609,  -- Anyway, I'll be gettin' my people on this. Uncle Riko'll find out what Toto is up to.
        IN_THE_MEANTIME_YA_BETTER_NOT_SPEAK_A                                 = 7610,  -- In the meantime, ya better not speak a word of this to no one, ya hear me?
        IF_NEWS_OF_TOTO_S_PLOT_WENT_PUBLIC                                    = 7611,  -- If news of Toto's plot went public, nobody would trust us Moogles ever again. That wouldn't be good for business. And what ain't good for Uncle Riko's business, ain't good for no one's business. Ya catch my drift, kid?
